nodes.text: Unidentified Human member of Grey Squadron

A Human male individual was a member of Grey Squadron, a New Republic military unit led by the Force-sensitive clone X2. At some point between the years 4 ABY and 19 ABY, the Human accompanied X2 and the rest of Grey Squadron on a mission to the planet Dathomir. There, the Human assisted X2 in clearing out the base that had once belonged to X2's brother, X1.
